| Tracy 2.8 | PHP 7.2 – 8.1
| Tracy 2.6 – 2.7 | PHP 7.1 – 8.0
| Tracy 2.5 | PHP 5.4 – 7.4
| Tracy 2.4 | PHP 5.4 – 7.2

